snippet.title: Animus Toil | Launch Trailer (Game Boy, PC)
snippet.description:
PROCEED WITH CURIOSITY.

#AnimusToil, our debut experimental puzzle-adventure game for Game Boy and PC, is available NOW!

Dive deep into the illusive Temple of the Herring, uncover the mysterious pieces that are scattered through its corridors, and take down the evil wizard Somnus.

https://mindsetmakers.itch.io/animus-toil

#gameboy #indie #indiegame
